    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a hallmark of BMW M-division engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain that delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed VANOS system, ensuring the chassis and variable valve timing are optimized for performance. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its communicative damping, providing exceptional lateral grip and feedback. This is a true driver's car, offering a visceral, analog experience with all major mechanical vulnerabilities addressed.",
