      "description": "This vehicle presents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for and reliable driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, accented by well-maintained alloy wheels; there is only minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, discreet scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort. The premium upholstery shows light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster but remains free of tears or stains, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust and inspires confidence. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, resulting in a smooth, responsive engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly. Garage-kept and smoke-free, this car offers a complete package of aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity, ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
